&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively with compliance teammates and leaders to ensure that issues are flagged to facilitate resolution, maintain quality, and drive key performance indicators.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete all required training and collaborate with compliance leadership to maintain knowledge and quality on all QA workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet productivity and quality targets established by leadership to achieve team and business needs&lt;/li&gt;
