&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of full-stack software development experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong React skills and knowledge of front end best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of Computer Science fundamentals such as relational databases, data structure and algorithms, Object Relational Mapping, REST APIs, microservices, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
